# ADR

Формат: **Context → Decision → Consequences → Status**

- Нумерация: `ADR-NNN-short-title.md`
- Связь со schemas: `docs/concept/schemas/`
- Статус: proposed | accepted | deprecated
- После accepted — обновить `docs/ROADMAP.md`
